rce_DxSubUnits.cmd:
set hive.exec.dynamic.partition.mode = nonstrict;set hive.execution.engine = tez;set tez.queue.name = default;
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS $DO__HV_DILAB_DM_TGT_SRC_TESTDATA_SIMPLE 
 (EMP_ID bigint
,DEPT_ID smallint
,FIRST_NAME varchar(50)
,LAST_NAME varchar(50)
,COMPANY_NAME varchar(100)
,JOIN_DATE date
,STANDARD_HOURS tinyint
,ACTIVE varchar(5)
,ADDRESS varchar(100)
,CITY varchar(50)
,COUNTRY varchar(50)
,STATE char(20)
,ZIP int
,PHONE1 varchar(50)
,PHONE2 varchar(50)
,EMAIL varchar(150)
,WEB varchar(2000)
)ROW FORMAT DELIMITED
FIELDS TERMINATED BY '01'
COLLECTION ITEMS TERMINATED BY '\002'
MAP KEYS TERMINATED BY '\003'
LINES TERMINATED BY '\n'
NULL DEFINED AS ''
STORED AS ORC
TBLPROPERTIES (
'orc.compress' = 'ZLIB',
'orc.stripe.size' = '268435456',
'orc.row.index.stride' = '10000',
'orc.create.index' = 'false',
'orc.compress.size' = '262144')
